data.description: Welcome to Santa Ynez Ave, where charm meets functionality in this delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence. Situated on a generous 0.29-acre lot, this 1,378 square foot home offers a perfect blend of comfort and style. Upon entering, you are greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere highlighted by a charming fireplace, creating the perfect focal point for cozy evenings with family and friends. The spacious living area provides an ideal setting for relaxation, entertaining, and creating lasting memories. The well-designed kitchen boasting ample storage space. The property's appeal extends beyond the walls of the house, as it is nestled in a nice neighborhood that enhances the overall sense of community and tranquility.
